I’ve been lurking around here for a few months, so this is a long overdue intro :stuck_out_tongue:

My name’s Braveen. I’m currently a Content Marketing Lead at Superside where I’m building out a squad focused on the bottom of our funnel.

Before that, I spent almost 6 years on the content team at Shopify where I was a senior IC.

My fun fact? I accidentally became an <https://www.braveenkumar.com/instagram-poet/|Instagram Poet>—with a real poetry book and small fanbase—because I wanted to see how far I could make it writing complete nonsense.

Happy to connect with like-minded folks :slightly_smiling_face:  (hit me up on LinkedIn or Twitter @braveenk)

Hi everyone! My name is Colleen and I'm managing editor at a large daily news company in Atlantic Canada. I'm here to explore the fresh ideas and opportunities out there in content, content marketing, digital strategy and product design. I love to build things, I love to tell stories and collaboration is my rocket fuel. As a journalist I know a little about a lot of different topics, but my niche personal interests are holistic health, sport and high performance, start ups and climate. Oh, and pop culture. That's my Jeopardy category jam. Feeling grateful to have stumbled upon this amazing group of likeminded people and like others, can't wait to learn and grow with you. :rocket:

If anyone out there is a journalist who has left the industry or a current one who is looking to make the leap, I'd love to connect.
